<plot>The first series of its kind, Quiet Mind introduces audiences to the living traditions of meditation in a visually rich and imaginative style. Through the use of fascinating characters, practical information, and real-life examples, Quiet Mind examines how ancient practices apply to our contemporary, fast-paced lives.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?452124</url></doc>
